{"tid":208520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"升職後訂單由下屬跟進 專業旅運前主任認向對方索回佣","createTime":"2017-04-19T14:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T16:25:32.000Z","uid":53403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68289ecab8595605359215dc2511a7b9b507baac","tid":208520,"uid":53403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"升職後訂單由下屬跟進 專業旅運前主任認向對方索回佣<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-04-19 13:16:10 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n專業旅運前櫃枱主任獲晉升後，將原由自己負責的訂單轉介給女下屬，下屬因而獲約6,100元佣金，前主任為此向她索取5,100元回佣，廉署接報後拘控前主任索賄罪，他今在東區法院認罪，裁判官下令索閱其感化及社會服務令報告，將他還柙至下月2日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳賢傑(34歲)負責監督銅鑼灣分行的營運，他於去年3月31日至5月6日期間犯案。辯方求情指陳自2010年加入專業旅運任初級旅遊顧問，去年2月晉升為櫃枱主任，月入2.5萬元，被捕後已離開專業旅運。被告妻子於求情信中盛讚被告是好丈夫，事後她需要接受心理輔導。辯方又指被告須照顧年老父親及祖母，他明知有判監可能但仍選擇認罪，望裁判官能視作例外情況而予以輕判。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56583907&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56583907%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170419&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a37af0d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56583907%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170419&h=d56a8832\" target=\"_blank\">hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56583907&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170419</a>"},{"pid":"b868c85837672b658ec857a0d34060ce35eb77da","tid":208520,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"做咩d單要益人"},{"pid":"8a2f486db7ca493f48d72261aef7aaa0442e51d6","tid":208520,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩d單要益人</blockquote><br />\n可能坐主任個位唔可以開單掛"},{"pid":"bf47d7443adf6551ecd2c46a318e37311b9ed419","tid":208520,"uid":53403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"女下屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebfe5a9c592351e2f8625f69e2b74e738687100","tid":208520,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女下屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}